Author:
Vasiliy Pogoreliy, vasiliy.6393@gmail.com

Dependences:
x11-misc/gtkdialog
app-misc/screen

Optional dependences:
gnome-extra/zenity

Install:
mkdir /emerzo (if you change this path, you must change the scripts)
cd /emerzo
tar xvf /path/to/emerzo.tar ./

Launch:
/emerzo/main.sh

